sun.jvm.hotspot.debugger.win32.coff

Interface DebugDirectoryEntry


  • public interface DebugDirectoryEntry
    Models an entry in the Debug Directory, which is an entry in the image optional header. This directory indicates where in the image the CodeView debug information appears, if enabled using /Z7 /PDB:NONE. (Some of the descriptions are taken directly from Microsoft's documentation and are copyrighted by Microsoft.)
